_ 整数算术
3 5 + :print

_ 浮点算术
3.0 5.0 + :print

_ 栈效应验证
@ add1 l:l 1 + ;
3 add1 :print

_ 条件分支（单词元分支）
@ neg d:d 0.0 :swap - ;
@ abs d:d :dup 0.0 < ? neg ! ;
-3.0 abs :print
3.0 abs :print

_ 递归 fib
@ fib d:d :dup 2.0 < ? $ :dup 1.0 - fib :swap 2.0 - fib + ;
1.0 fib :print
2.0 fib :print
5.0 fib :print
10.0 fib :print
35.0 fib :print
